title: Nomination of the Honorable Neil M. Gorsuch to be an Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States (Day 2)
text:
Hart Senate Office Building 216 Presiding: 
A video of the hearing will be available here once the hearing begins. Agenda March 20, 2017 NOTICE OF COMMITTEE HEARING CONTINUATION The Senate Committee on the Judiciary hearing on the nomination of the Honorable Neil M. Gorsuch to be an Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States will continue March 21, 2017 at 9:30 a.m. in Room 216 of the Hart Senate Office Building. By order of the Chairman. Witness List Senate Committee on the Judiciary on The Nomination of Neil M. Gorsuch to be an Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States Monday, March 20, 2017 Hart Senate Office Building, Room 216 11:00 a.m.
